Interface Summary
IAeBpelAdmin Describes the interface used for interacting with a business process engine
IAeRemoteDebugConstants Constants used for administrative web services on both stub and skeltons.
 

Class Summary
AeAddAttachmentResponse Java bean to hold the response of an add attachment request
AeAttachmentAttribute JavaBean for holding some data for a single attachment attribute definition.

AeBreakpointList Wrapper for the list of breakpoints sent by the designer during remote debugging.
AeRemoteDebugImpl Remote implementation of the BPEL Engine used by Web Service invocation.

AeRemoteDebugImpl.AeRemoteResumeWork Scheduled work for resuming a process.
AeRemoteDebugImpl.AeRemoteSuspendWork Scheduled work for suspending a process.
AeRemoteDebugImpl.AeRemoteTerminateWork Scheduled work for terminating a process.
AeRemoteDebugImpl.AeRemoteWork Base class for our work involving calls into the engine that affect a process.
